media: v4l: Add definitions for missing 16-bit RGB555 formats

The V4L2 API is missing the 16-bit RGB555 formats for the RGBA, RGBX,
ABGR, XBGR, BGRA and BGRX component orders. Add them, using the same
4CCs as DRM.

